snippet: Less than two weeks after pulling out of the Paris Masters semi-finals with a thigh injury, Milos Raonic reached the last four at the ATP World Tour Finals and is close to breaking into the top three of the rankings....
lead_paragraph: Less than two weeks after pulling out of the Paris Masters semi-finals with a thigh injury, Milos Raonic reached the last four at the ATP World Tour Finals and is close to breaking into the top three of the rankings.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Chases Top Three Spot After Win Over Thiem
headline.main: Raonic Chases Top Three Spot After Win Over Thiem
